<br>
With due consideration of the fact that it really bites to die for no good reason and lose a night's work, this looks to me like OOTT (One Of Those Things), with a side order of rudeness.  I've been in a few groups like that that seem fated to lead to death.  It's amazing how this game permits people to survive when they seem to be completely ignorant of how to play (unlike us, of course <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> ).  <br>
